To-do List v.0.2 (ะก++)
This program created by using procedural programming.

This is console to-do list with simple menu and next functions:
  -  See notes
  -  Find note
  -  Write new note
  -  Delete note
  -  Change note
  -  Clear to-do list
 
 
Known bugs/flaws:
  - "Change note" section:
    1) If user selects note for changing and than enter void string the note will be deleted


Fixed bugs/flaws:
  - "Change note" section:
    1) If user enters void string the program will crash ("debug error, abort() has been called")
